Speaker: 
https://christopheradams.io/

Christopher Adams is a software developer specializing in distributed systems and blockchain applications, and a publisher and photographer focused on free culture. He is chief architect at Fabricatorz, a global art technology and design studio, and has presented his work at Ars Electronica, transmediale, and Impakt Festival.  He is also a primary contributor to the #NEWPALMYRA project. He is based in Taipei.
